acpi-support (0.143-5) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Debian Janitor ]
  * Add missing Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends} in acpi-support.

  [ Josue Ortega ]
  * Remove tab characters from debian/control
  * Add support for cinnamon-screen-saver. Closes: #822620
  * Fix FTCBFS, thanks to Helmut Grohne <helmut@subdivi.de>
    for the patch: (Closes: #897093)
    + Let dh_auto_build pass cross tools to make.
    + Allow substituting build tools in fakekey Makefile.

 -- Josue Ortega <josue@debian.org>  Sun, 19 Apr 2020 11:28:23 -0600

acpi-support (0.143-4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add condicion to check for AC Power in acpi-support.serice. Thanks
    to Shannon Brady for the patch <shannonbrady@google.com> Closes: #946600
  * Remove pm-powersave invocation from debian/addons/scripts/power.sh.
    pm-powersave is no longer a package dependency. Closes: #940158
  * Bump Standards-Version to 4.4.1. No changes required
  * debian/control: Add Rules-Requires-Root field

 -- Josue Ortega <josue@debian.org>  Mon, 30 Dec 2019 15:14:11 -0600

acpi-support (0.143-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * debian/acpi-fakekey.socket: Update ListenFIFO path to use
    /run/acpi_fakekey instead of legacy /var/run. Closes: #932104
  * Drop pm-utils dependendency. Thanks to Michael Biebl
    <biebl@debian.org> for the patch. Closes: #931689
