acpi-support (0.138-8) unstable; urgency=low

  * Create fifo under /var/run instead of using shared memory as filesystem.
    (Closes: #616023)
  * The kernel might give a tty number despite running on a serial line. Make
    sure the scripts can cope with this. (Closes: #612849)
  * Removed old workaround needed when acpi-fakekey became its own package
    because squeeze was released with acpi-fakekey package. (Closes: #613901)

